  Locus:
    Page: 503
    Verse: 14
Tags:
  - Work
---
Do your work in the world, but inwardly keep quiet. Then all will come to
you. Do not rely on your own work for realization. It may profit others
but not you. Your hope lies in keeping silent in your mind and quiet in
your heart.
